open git bash

To know what is the current folder
    pwd (present working directory)

To list the contents of the directory
    ls (list)

Use "cd" to go to the application folder (ensure "master" is displayed)
    Hint:
        to go to the parent folder
            cd ..


To know the changes made
    git status

To add the changes
    git add .

To confirm the changes
    git commit -m "give a meaningful comment"

To push the changes to github
    git push
